==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fanaticism
<hw>Fa*nat"i*cism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Fanatism</er>.]</ety> <def>Excessive enthusiasm, unreasoning zeal,
or wild and extravagant notions, on any subject, especially religion,
politics or ideology; religious frenzy.</def></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- See <er>Superstition</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fanaticize</ent>⟦br⟧
